### 用 JWT 发消息（把登录返回的 token 填进去）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json
# Authorization: Bearer 这里填登录返回的token
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOjEsImlhdCI6MTc4MjExNjQ4OCwiZXhwIjoxNzgyNzIxMjg4fQ.wzH2pwcfPPwMI9L1Uwo3Z1nsJYzPuDh93XUTy1vEk9w

{
  "message": "你好",
  "sessionId": "test-jwt-1"
}